caption.title: Fitted Parameters for Q-learning model from PyStan.
caption.p: 25th, 50th, and 75th percentile of the alpha, beta, and stay parameters of the Q-learning mixed effect model. These are the the group-level parameters that reflect the distribution of the subject-level parameters.

caption.title: Mixed effect Q-learning model parameters.
caption.p: Parameters from the mixed effect Q-learning model, including group-level and individual-level parameters, and the mean and range of data across samples from the model. See 'Q Learning Mixed Effect Model' in the Materials and methods section for more details.
